data.description: This 3BR/2BA, 1,200 sq ft under air renovated Fairmont boasts a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, glass tile backsplash, Samsung stainless appliances, and a seating island for casual dining. Ceramic tile floors throughout, new laminate flooring in the bedrooms. Recessed lighting, accordion shutters, hurricane garage rated door. New A/C with ALL new duct pipes, separate split A/C in the garage, Rheem Performance instant water heater, Siemens panel. 2/2022 Tent treatment. 6/2022 freshly painted, roof pressure washed, painted, and sealed. 20ft double wide driveway. Extra cabinet space in the bedrooms. Tons of amenities for 55+, all included for a low $167/month HOA fee! Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to call this house your home!
